{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-21\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/callCard.ts","offset":120,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"/** ScheduleCard 形态守卫：cardKind 必须为 schedule */\nexport function isScheduleCard(\n  card: CallCardDefinition,\n): card is CallCardDefinition & { cardKind: \"schedule\" } {\n  return card.cardKind === \"schedule\";\n}\n\nexport const StoryPackageConfSchema = z.object({\n  schemaVersion: z.number().int(),\n  packageId: z.string(),\n  title: z.string().optional(),\n  /** 遗留白名单；路径 B 下磁盘可省略，解析后缺省为 [] */\n  participants: z.array(z.string()).optional().default([]),\n  entryCardId: z.string().optional(),\n  /** 本包引用的全局 assetId（导出子集）；非第二真源 */\n  assetRefs: z.array(z.string()).optional(),\n  cards: z\n    .array(z.object({ cardId: z.string() }).passthrough())\n    .default([]),\n});\n\nexport type StoryPackageConf = z.infer<typeof StoryPackageConfSchema>;\n\nexport function formatZodError(err: z.ZodError): string {\n  return err.issues\n    .map(function (issue) {\n      const path = issue.path.length > 0 ? issue.path.join(\".\") : \"(root)\";\n      return `${path}: ${issue.message}`;\n    })\n    .join(\"; \");\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":151,"fileSize":4827,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/packages/rpg-engine/src/schema/callCard.ts","readRange":{"startLine":120,"endLine":151},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-21\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_0","startedAtMs":"1784769164298","completedAtMs":"1784769164520"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-5-tsbm","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769164479}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-25\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_4","tool_call":{"grepToolCall":{"args":{"pattern":"worldFacts|assetRefs|StoryPackage|meta","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","caseInsensitive":false,"multiline":false,"toolCallId":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-25\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_4","offset":0},"result":{"success":{"pattern":"worldFacts|assetRefs|StoryPackage|meta","path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","outputMode":"content","workspaceResults":{"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine":{"content":{"matches":[{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":13,"content":"| 静态 | `CallCardDefinition` | 写在 StoryPackage 里；可版本化、可编辑 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":373,"content":"## 8. StoryPackage（静态包）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":376,"content":"interface StoryPackage {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":388,"content":"  worldFacts?: FactMeta[]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":391,"content":"  assetRefs?: string[]","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":392,"content":"  meta?: {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":6,"totalMatchedLines":6,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-25\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_4","startedAtMs":"1784769164309","completedAtMs":"1784769164520"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-5-tsbm","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769164479}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-24\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 01. CallCard 数据模型\n\n本文定义 CallCard 体系的静态与运行时数据结构。实现时以 Zod（或等价）schema 为真源；本文为需求级描述。\n\n**存档口径**：`CallCardInstance` / `CallCardBoard` 挂在当前用户的 [PlayerProfile](./10-用户与存档.md) 下，不是全局单例。\n\n相关：[02-运行时协议](./02-运行时协议.md) · [11-角色与社交](./11-角色与社交.md) · [07-壳嵌入与导出契约](../技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md)\n\n## 1. 两层对象\n\n| 层 | 类型 | 说明 |\n|----|------|------|\n| 静态 | `CallCardDefinition` | 写在 StoryPackage 里；可版本化、可编辑 |\n| 运行时 | `CallCardInstance` | 挂在某角色身上；带 status 与来源 |\n\n**禁止**把运行状态写回 Definition。同一张 Definition 可在不同 StoryInstance / 模拟中产生多个 Instance。\n\n## 2. CallCardDefinition\n\n```ts\ntype CardKind = \"free\" | \"story\" | \"system\"\ntype InteractionMode = \"realtime_dialogue\" | \"playback_only\" | \"hybrid\"\ntype EntryMode = \"inbound_user_dial\" | \"outbound_auto\" | \"either\"\n\ninterface CallCardDefinition {\n  cardId: string\n  cardKind: CardKind\n  title: string\n  ownerAgentId: string\n  entryMode: EntryMode\n  interactionMode: InteractionMode\n\n  context: CallCardContext\n  objectives: CallCardObjectives\n  toolPolicy: ToolPolicy\n  assets?: CardAssets\n\n  exits: CallCardExit[]\n}\n```\n\n### 2.1 cardKind\n\n| 值 | 含义 |\n|----|------|\n| `free` | 自由通话默认卡；每角色应有且仅有一份默认 FreeCallCard（可在角色库配置） |\n| `story` | 强约束剧情卡 |\n| `system` | 系统/媒介卡（过场播放、系统提示等） |\n\n### 2.2 entryMode","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":432,"fileSize":16127,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-5b1ee12c-8869-40b6-9c86-3101bcb673f9-24\nfc_c3feb00a-6c88-9ff2-a8ca-a20dae611763_3","startedAtMs":"1784769164306","completedAtMs":"1784769164521"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-5-tsbm","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769164481}
