","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":83,"content":"  factId?: string","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":112,"content":"相对旧模型：层少、可过期、可对齐 factId、写入路径统一；**生活边角与通末总结统一进 episodic**，不再另开 shared_memories 仓。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":189,"content":"- Semantic 可引用 `factId`，避免两套真相；**升格为世界事实必须走** `set_world_fact`。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":12,"totalMatchedLines":12,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-e2b81a77-c855-46b0-b605-b740db143cf6-38\nfc_f35e1083-b9cb-9dd7-b013-78e029b46825_2","startedAtMs":"1784769176812","completedAtMs":"1784769177037"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-8-fbjd","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769177004}
