{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-c182e378-8821-43d7-86c5-cf44aac1f6e1-44\nfc_52f69ebc-03f1-9ddf-822e-9c2a0c0dabe5_2","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/StoryEditorShell.tsx"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 故事编辑器全屏壳：画布为主角 + 底栏 + 属性/资源/包配置浮窗。\n\t* 角色入口仅画布锚点（新建/编辑复用 /characters FormModal）；包读写经 /api/stories。\n\t*/\n\"use client\";\n\nimport type { FC } from \"react\";\nimport { Alert, CircularProgress, Typography } from \"@mui/material\";\nimport { StoryEditorTopBar } from \"@studio-v2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/StoryEditorTopBar\";\nimport { BottomToolBar } from \"@studio-v2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/BottomToolBar\";\n// 引用了StoryEditorCanvasLayer组件，用于画布与浮窗叠层\nimport { StoryEditorCanvasLayer } from \"@studio-v2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/com/shell/StoryEditorCanvasLayer\";\n// 引用了StoryEditorShellModals组件，用于角色/资源/节点删除弹层\nimport { StoryEditorShellModals } from \"@studio-v2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/com/shell/StoryEditorShellModals\";\nimport { useStoryEditorShellController } from \"@studio-v2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/hooks/shell/useStoryEditorShellController\";\nimport styles from \"./StoryEditorShell.module.scss\";\n\nexport type StoryEditorShellProps = {\n\t/** 路由包键；打开与保存均针对 data/storis-packages 下该目录 */\n\tpackageId: string;\n};\n\nexport const StoryEditorShell: FC<StoryEditorShellProps> = function ({\n\t// packageId 是路由包键，用于磁盘整包读写\n\tpackageId,\n}) {\n\tconst shell = useStoryEditorShellController(packageId);\n\tconst { characterForms, assetForms, packageSession } = shell;\n\tconst { loading, loadError, graphSeed, saveState, saveError, onSave, bundle } =\n\t\tpackageSession;\n\n\tif (loading) {\n\t\treturn (\n\t\t\t<div className={styles.root}>\n\t\t\t\t<div className={styles.loadingWrap}>\n\t\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了CircularProgress组件，用于加载指示 */}\n\t\t\t\t\t<CircularProgress size={32} />\n\t\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了Typography组件，用于加载说明 */}\n\t\t\t\t\t<Typography variant=\"body2\">正在从磁盘加载故事包…</Typography>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t);\n\t}\n\n\tif (loadError || !graphSeed || !bundle) {\n\t\treturn (\n\t\t\t<div className={styles.root}>\n\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了Alert组件，用于加载失败提示 */}\n\t\t\t\t<Alert severity=\"error\" className={styles.loadError}>\n\t\t\t\t\t{loadError ?? \"无法加载故事包\"}\n\t\t\t\t</Alert>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t);\n\t}\n\n\treturn (\n\t\t<div className={styles.root}>\n\t\t\t{/* 引用了StoryEditorTopBar组件，用于顶栏包名与保存 */}\n\t\t\t<StoryEditorTopBar\n\t\t\t\tpackageTitle={shell.packageTitle}\n\t\t\t\tchapterTitle={bundle.conf.title ?? \"章节\"}\n\t\t\t\tsaveState={saveState}\n\t\t\t\tsaveError={saveError}\n\t\t\t\tonSave={function () {\n\t\t\t\t\tvoid onSave();\n\t\t\t\t}}\n\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t<div className={styles.body}>\n\t\t\t\t{/* 引用了StoryEditorCanvasLayer组件，用于画布与浮窗叠层 */}\n\t\t\t\t<StoryEditorCanvasLayer\n\t\t\t\t\tpackageId={packageId}\n\t\t\t\t\tgraphSeed={graphSeed}\n\t\t\t\t\tbundle={bundle}\n\t\t\t\t\tselection={shell.selection}\n\t\t\t\t\tassetFloat={shell.assetFloat}\n\t\t\t\t\tpackageFloat={shell.packageFloat}\n\t\t\t\t\tassets={assetForms.assets}\n\t\t\t\t\tcharacterAnchors={shell.characterAnchors}\n\t\t\t\t\teffectPanelSources={shell.effectPanelSources}\n\t\t\t\t\tchapterDiskCtx={shell.chapterDiskCtx}\n\t\t\t\t\tchapterPackageOptions={shell.chapterPackageOptions}\n\t\t\t\t\tonSelectionChange={shell.onSelectionChange}\n\t\t\t\t\tonCharacterAnchorSelect={shell.onCharacterAnchorSelect}\n\t\t\t\t\tonCanvasReady={shell.onCanvasReady}\n\t\t\t\t\tonGraphMetaChange={shell.onGraphMetaChange}\n\t\t\t\t\tonToolModeChange={shell.onToolModeChange}\n\t\t\t\t\tonApplyNodeData={shell.onApplyNodeData}\n\t\t\t\t\tonApplyChapterNodeData={shell.onApplyChapterNodeData}\n\t\t\t\t\tonAssignOwner={shell.onAssignOwner}\n\t\t\t\t\tonRequestDeleteNode={shell.onRequestDeleteNode}\n\t\t\t\t\tonAddCharacter={characterForms.openCreate}\n\t\t\t\t\tonCloseSelection={shell.closeSelection}\n\t\t\t\t\tonCloseAssetFloat={shell.closeAssetFloat}\n\t\t\t\t\tonClosePackageFloat={shell.closePackageFloat}\n\t\t\t\t\tonCreateAsset={assetForms.openCreate}\n\t\t\t\t\tonEditAsset={assetForms.openEdit}\n\t\t\t\t\tonRequestDeleteAsset={assetForms.onRequestDelete}\n\t\t\t\t\tentryCardOptions={shell.entryCardOptions}\n\t\t\t\t\tonEntryCardIdChange={packageSession.onEntryCardIdChange}\n\t\t\t\t\tonAssetRefsChange={packageSession.onAssetRefsChange}\n\t\t\t\t\tcanUseAsPlaybackClip={shell.canUseAsPlaybackClip}\n\t\t\t\t\tonUseAsPlaybackClip={shell.onUseAsPlaybackClip}\n\t\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t{/* 引用了BottomToolBar组件，用于底栏工具模式与资源/包入口 */}\n\t\t\t<BottomToolBar\n\t\t\t\tactiveToolId={shell.activeToolId}\n\t\t\t\tonToolClick={shell.onToolClick}\n\t\t\t\tchapterEndDisabled={shell.chapterEndDisabled}\n\t\t\t\tonOpenAssets={shell.openAssetsFloat}\n\t\t\t\tonOpenPackage={shell.openPackageFloat}\n\t\t\t\tassetsActive={shell.assetFloat}\n\t\t\t\tpackageActive={shell.packageFloat}\n\t\t\t/>\n\t\t\t{/* 引用了StoryEditorShellModals组件，用于角色/资源/节点删除弹层 */}\n\t\t\t<StoryEditorShellModals\n\t\t\t\tcharacter={characterForms}\n\t\t\t\tasset={assetForms}\n\t\t\t\tpendingDeleteNode={shell.pendingDelete}\n\t\t\t\tonCloseDeleteNode={shell.closeDeleteNodeModal}\n\t\t\t\tonConfirmDeleteNode={shell.onConfirmDeleteNode}\n\t\t\t/>\n\t\t</div>\n\t);\n};\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":126,"fileSize":4934,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/StoryEditorShell.tsx","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":126},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-c182e378-8821-43d7-86c5-cf44aac1f6e1-44\nfc_52f69ebc-03f1-9ddf-822e-9c2a0c0dabe5_2","startedAtMs":"1784769187127","completedAtMs":"1784769187420"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-9-utrh","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769187397}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-c182e378-8821-43d7-86c5-cf44aac1f6e1-42\nfc_52f69ebc-03f1-9ddf-822e-9c2a0c0dabe5_0","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/conf/referencedAgentsDerive.ts"},"result":{"success":{"content":"/**\n\t* 路径 B：本包引用角色派生（lanes / 包配置 / 列表 characterCount）。\n\t* 真源 = collectReferencedAgentIds；禁止手维 conf.participants 白名单。\n\t*/\nimport {\n\tcollectReferencedAgentIds,\n\ttype CallCardDefinition,\n\ttype StoryPackageConf,\n} from \"@airpc/rpg-engine\";\n\n/** conf+cards 切片；layout 不参与派生 */\nexport type ReferencedAgentsBundleSlice = {\n\t/** 包 conf；仅作引擎 collect 入参壳，派生不读 participants */\n\tconf: StoryPackageConf;\n\t/** 本包已加载 CallCard；owner/effects 为引用真源 */\n\tcards: readonly CallCardDefinition[];\n};\n\n/** 有挂卡（owner）者排前，其余引用角色随后；稳定去重 */\nfunction sortUsedOwnersFirst(\n\tagentIds: readonly string[],\n\tcards: readonly CallCardDefinition[],\n): string[] {\n\tconst used: string[] = [];\n\tconst unused: string[] = [];\n\tfor (const agentId of agentIds) {\n\t\tconst hasOwnerCard = cards.some(function (c) {\n\t\t\treturn c.ownerAgentId === agentId;\n\t\t});\n\t\tif (hasOwnerCard) used.push(agentId);\n\t\telse unused.push(agentId);\n\t}\n\treturn [...used, ...unused];\n}\n\n/**\n\t* 本包内容引用的 agentId 列表（有卡者优先）。\n\t* 与引擎 validate 口径一致；遗留 participants 不入集。\n\t*/\nexport function listDerivedReferencedAgentIds(\n\tbundle: ReferencedAgentsBundleSlice,\n): string[] {\n\tconst ids = [\n\t\t...collectReferencedAgentIds({\n\t\t\tconf: bundle.conf,\n\t\t\tcards: [...bundle.cards],\n\t\t}),\n\t];\n\treturn sortUsedOwnersFirst(ids, bundle.cards);\n}\n\n/** Studio layout.lanes：按派生引用角色写序；引擎忽略 */\nexport function deriveLayoutLanes(\n\tbundle: ReferencedAgentsBundleSlice,\n): Array<{ agentId: string; order: number }> {\n\treturn listDerivedReferencedAgentIds(bundle).map(function (agentId, order) {\n\t\treturn { agentId, order };\n\t});\n}\n\n/**\n\t* 保存写盘：去掉遗留 participants，避免再落白名单字段。\n\t* 内存/Zod 解析仍可有缺省 []；磁盘推荐省略键。\n\t*/\nexport function omitParticipantsForDiskWrite(\n\tconf: StoryPackageConf,\n): Omit<StoryPackageConf, \"participants\"> & {\n\tparticipants?: undefined;\n} {\n\tconst { participants: _legacy, ...rest } = conf;\n\tvoid _legacy;\n\treturn rest;\n}\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":74,"fileSize":2173,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/apps/studioV2/src/bis/pageBis/storyEditor/package/conf/referencedAgentsDerive.ts","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":74},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-c182e378-8821-43d7-86c5-cf44aac1f6e1-42\nfc_52f69ebc-03f1-9ddf-822e-9c2a0c0dabe5_0","startedAtMs":"1784769187121","completedAtMs":"1784769187420"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-9-utrh","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769187398}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-c182e378-8821-43d7-86c5-cf44aac1f6e1-45\nfc_52f69ebc-03f1-9ddf-822e-9c2a0c0dabe5_3","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/03-故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗.md","limit":80},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗（代码事实）\n\n> 对照：`apps/studioV2/src/pageComponents/storyEditor/**` + `bis/pageBis/storyEditor/**`。  \n> UI 向导需求：[02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿](../../AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/02-新版故事编辑器界面UI设计向导稿.md)。  \n> Effect 面板细化：[细化修改7_需求](../../AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改7_需求.md)。  \n> 固化：2026-07-22（V2-T3-8：打开读盘 + 整包保存 + 编辑接线落盘）。\n\n## 1. 壳层结构（认知地图）\n\n```text\nStoryEditorShell\n  ├ StoryEditorTopBar          # chapterTitle 等；保存 → saveStoryPackage_bis\n  ├ StoryEditorCanvasLayer     # React Flow 舞台\n  │    └ StoryCanvasStage / useStoryCanvasGraph\n  ├ FloatingPanelShell         # 属性浮窗（可拖、粘性头尾）\n  │    ├ NodePropertyForm | ChapterPropertyForm\n  │    └ ExitListEditor → ExitEffectsList → ExitEffectPanel\n  ├ BottomToolBar              # placement：CallCard / chapter_end …\n  └ library floats             # 包配置 / 资源挑选等\n```\n\n会话态：节点/边在 `useStoryCanvasGraph` 的 React state；**顶栏保存**经 `editorGraphToBundle` 写回 `data/storis-packages`。\n\n## 2. 节点种类\n\n| React Flow type | data 投影 | 作用 |\n|-----------------|-----------|------|\n| `callCard` | `EditorCallCardProjection` | 通话合同卡 |\n| `chapter` | `EditorChapterNodeData` | `chapter_start` / `chapter_end` |\n| `characterAnchor` | `CharacterAnchorNodeData` | 左侧角色锚点；role handle |\n\n另有轻量 dock 节点（action / commentGroup）：可放置，但属性浮窗策略与 CallCard 分离（见 dock 工厂）。\n\n## 3. 边种类\n\n| edgeKind | 视觉意图 | 真源 |\n|----------|----------|------|\n| `story` | 章节/出口流转（实线） | layout.edges + 会话内连线 |\n| `role` | 卡 → 锚点归属（灰点线） | `ROLE_EDGE_STYLE` |\n| `effect` | attach/unmount（绿虚线等） | `effectEdgeSync.ts` 与 `exit.effects[]` 双向 |\n\n效果边 id：`effect_${sourceNodeId}_${exitId}_${effectId}`，须与 layout 种子边一致以便 reconcile 幂等。\n\n## 4. 选中与属性浮窗（铁律级行为）\n\n- **仅单选**节点打开属性浮窗：`storyCanvasSelection.ts` 中 `params.nodes.length === 1`。  \n- **框选多节点不得开浮窗**（曾出岔子，见 [06](./06-过程岔子与纠正记录.md)）。  \n- `selectionKind`：`callCard` | `chapter`；锚点走角色 FormModal，不是 CallCard 浮窗。  \n- 防御：`toolPolicy?.mode ?? \"\"` 等，避免缺字段炸表单。\n\n## 5. 出口与 Effect 面板\n\n- 出口列表：`ExitListEditor` / `exitListForm`。  \n- Effect 参数联合：`typeFiles/.../editorEffectParams.ts`（按 effect 判别，禁 catchall）。  \n- 面板注册：`ExitEffectPanel.tsx` → 各 `*EffectPanel`。  \n- 摘要文案：`summarizeEffect.ts`。  \n- 挂载目标：Mount 弹层只选**目标卡**，`agentId` 由卡归属推导（曾简化，见 06）。\n\n第一幕磁盘包常用 effect：`attach_call_card`、`schedule_call_card`、`create_voicemail`、`end_story`。\n\n## 6. 浮窗拖拽\n\n- `hooks/panel/useFloatingPanelDrag.ts`。  \n- 坐标相对 **`offsetParent`**，不是 viewport 裸 client（曾偏位，见 06）。\n\n## 7. 打开 / 保存管道\n\n- **打开：** `loadStoryPackageForEditor` → `GET /api/stories/:id` → `bundleToEditorGraph` → 初始 nodes/edges。  \n- **保存：** 顶栏 → `saveStoryPackageToDisk` → `editorGraphToBundle` → `PUT /api/stories/:id`。  \n- **默认包：** 路由 `wrong_number_act1`；缺 layout 时 BFF 安全默认坐标。  \n- 业务叙事：见 [04](./04-第一幕打错电话-mock拓扑.md)。\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":72,"fileSize":3710,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI/studio-v2/03-故事编辑器画布与属性浮窗.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":72},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-c182e378-8821-43d7-86c5-cf44aac1f6e1-45\nfc_52f69ebc-03f1-9ddf-822e-9c2a0c0dabe5_3","startedAtMs":"1784769187130","completedAtMs":"1784769187423"},"model_call_id":"9a82b57f-cd94-4b73-ad8d-e1d7fd46b7ce-9-utrh","session_id":"c107c1ba-b725-44dc-b67c-eb2439bd913e","timestamp_ms":1784769187402}
